      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>SHER-Rose. On August 15, 2000. Poet, actress, playwright, performer, mother of Daniel, Richard and Mark. Also survived by grandsons Martin and Jonathan. ''Don't worry about me 'cause I'm 'Lost in the Stars' with Kurt Weill and Thee Oh God.'' Service Friday, August 18th at 2PM at ''The Riverside,'' 76th and Amsterdam Avenue.</p>
